# Docker Configuration Guide

## Purpose
- Define containerization for all services here
- Separate dev,sit,uat,nft and prod configurations
- Configure development environment
- Setup production-ready containers
- Manage database containers

## Requirements
- Separate dev,sit,uat,nft and prod configurations
- Multi-stage builds for efficiency
- Volume mounting for development
- Health checks
- Proper networking
- Centralize docker and docker-compose for all back end and front end services here
